cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.IT

The paper discusses the utilization of machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques for enhancing the efficiency of wireless network operation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also extensively discusses the utilization of AI principles, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely category as well. The paper also discusses the use of data analytics and natural language processing techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IT (Information Theory) likely categories. Finally, the paper discusses the integration of these techniques for designing a tightly integrated network, which makes cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category as well.
